FLASHStrategy This class implements the general strategy of the ARX algorithm.
 

Package org.deidentifier.arx.algorithm Description

This package provides algorithms which traverse the generalization lattice. An abstract base class can be utilized to implement novel algorithms within the anonymization framework.
